 the reality outside, inside and in between. This pure reality are like how our mind is

00:03:10.560 --> 00:03:15.680
 when wisdom is allowed to do what wisdom does. When compassion is allowed to flow is compassion

00:03:15.680 --> 00:03:21.480
 will. When we don't block that up, naturally flows wisdom and compassion. It's all pure

00:03:21.480 --> 00:03:49.600
