00:05:38.830 --> 00:05:39.120
 trying to

00:05:39.120 --> 00:05:45.120
 become more flexible and skillful with how we use them. So we can use these beliefs, these views,

00:05:45.120 --> 00:05:53.520
 these patterns to actually include more reality, more of nature, more of Dharma, more Yanas. That's

00:05:53.520 --> 00:05:57.760
 why the higher vehicles or Yanas include the lower Yanas and vehicles, but they transcend the

